
Just run the following command:

 packs formamide.gro water.gro -nm 2500 -cc 1.0 -it -bk

This will create:

 formamide+water_mol2500.gro
 formamide+water_mol2500.top
 formamide+water_mol2500.zip

To visualize the simulation box, try:

 sview formamide+water_mol2500.gro
 jmol formamide+water_mol2500.gro
 vmd formamide+water_mol2500.gro

To test the simulation box, try:

 mdrun formamide+water_mol2500.gro -chk

